Norris, K. (1996). The cloister walk. Riverhead. — On Benedictine silence from a non-monastic perspective.
Cooper, D. A. (1992). Silence, simplicity, and solitude: A guide for spiritual retreat. Bell Tower. — Practical, cross-traditional.
